name: Gray Squadron Y-wing Pilot
Lore: 'Veteran pilots of the reliable Koensayr starfigher were assigned by Ackbar to a key role at Endor. Both the pilots and their venerable Y-wings were up to the task.',
Text: 'Adds 2 to the power of anything he pilots. When piloting a Y-wing, draws one battle destiny if not able to otherwise. When a starship he pilots fires an ion cannon, once per turn, may draw two weapon destiny and choose one.',
